    <description>SP: V2 compatible for multiple ConsentFormTaken Records
FB: testing update sign employee id from consent form portal
FB: This version improves support for documents that require the ID of the doctor who signs in via SSO on the Titan Consent Form Portal.
The flow now accepts an optional parameter — the doctor’s ID (employee_id_from_titan) — and updates the signedEmployeeId field on the ConsentFormTaken object. This information is then added to the document.

FB: 26/10/2025 -  added the doctor name and the doctor code separately in the assignment node for the consentformtaken record variable update with the id from SSO
SP: 27112025 - Added RT get</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
